UInt32 Vps_VipPortDisConfig::actvidPol

For valid values see Fvid2_Polarity.

UInt32 Vps_VipPortDisConfig::discreteBasicMode

FALSE = Normal Discrete Mode, TRUE = Basic Discrete Mode. TRUE = DE signal need not be active during the VBLANK period. Most of the encoder provide the discrete signals in this way. FALSE = DE signal needs to be active during the VBLANK period.
